getValue
Class UserValue

java.lang.Object
  getValue.UserValue

public class UserValue
extends java.lang.Object

This class is used to obtain statistics about a user. Given the user's name and the location of the server database, a string with the specific statistic will be returned.

Author:
Nicholas Ingalls
